@emmachamberlain I know you use a tripod for your video, but there are phone holders that stick to your window that cost about $30. Truckers use them all the time for their videos. That way you won't have your camera falling over.
I watched your video of you cutting your gair. I was like .... Aaaaaaaahhhhhhh!!!!! Wait a minute... She's hot! You still look great with your gsir cut. Just I hope you don't go shorter. When you dyed it I didn't know it was you at first. Then came the wigs. Then it hit me. Tyra had a wo an cut her hair short so she could wear wigs & be versatile. Yes I watched Next Top Model all the time until they had the transgender on there. I completely stopped watching the show after that. Sorry if I upset anyone, but if I watch something for the women then that's what I expect to see. Women! I don't want to be guessing & drooling over something that I don't want. Everybody has their line drawn in the sand. That is my line.
I finally made it to my room in Fort Lauderdale. I needed the time off. Plus my birthday is Mobday. Would live to fly you in & meet you. But... I don't think you'd like hanging out with grandpa. I am so tired I dropped my phone several times while going over my DNA report. And while writing you. Tomorrow is soaking in the tub day & finding a sauna. Plus FINALLY getting to sweep & mop my truck! I tell you I get so busy running these loads I hardly have time to do anything else. Wish you coukd be here so I can enjoy your company.
